  "title": "今日开源（2026-1-15）：阶跃星辰双料开源！Step-Audio-R1.1 领跑语音推理，STEP3-VL 碾压千亿多模态模型",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247501359&idx=1&sn=1de0e5e9e22c59f7ecd25252acff1a43",
  "date": "2026-01-15 10:30:00",
