  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"text-align: center;line-height: normal;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"></span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"text-indent: 0px;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-indent: 0px;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：Step-Audio-R1.1</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"450\" data-imgfileid=\"100017702\" data-ratio=\"0.3888888888888889\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1158\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=23818a39&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzdY4WicrXJrlGN01A1QAH2pxXhzvIFZYA92s6bn5HMExCOqZd5ZSicraAM1EKmzMPAa5wALPTLrXRg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Step-Audio-R1.1是阶跃星辰推出的原生音频推理增强模型，以96.4%的准确率登顶全球权威语音推理榜单。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">模型优化了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">模态锚定推理蒸馏（MGRD）框架</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，进一步强化声学特征与推理链的绑定，彻底解决“推理越长性能越差”的反向扩展难题，同时通过</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">端到端架构</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">将首包延迟降低30%以上，支持“边想边说”的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">流式实时交互</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。其核心突破在于实现从</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">“识别语音”</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">到</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">“理解意图”</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">的跨越，能捕捉情绪语调、言外之意及环境音隐含信息，适配多语言与多方言场景，性能超越Grok、Gemini等国际一线模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/step-audio-r1\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/step-audio-r1</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：STEP3-VL</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"668\" data-imgfileid=\"100017704\" data-ratio=\"0.5768518518518518\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1158\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cdb4670d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzdY4WicrXJrlGN01A1QAH2pmn1LZ5CusCAhkBOMgV59ezBZ2gX3ibSkuPiclNRtMzoicdmQKIlKUUpug%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★STEP3-VL是一个轻量级的开源基础模型，旨在重新定义紧凑效率与前沿多模态智能之间的权衡。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">尽管其参数量仅为10B，但在</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">视觉感知、复杂推理</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">人类对齐</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">方面表现出色。它不仅在</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">10B规模以下的模型</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">中表现优异，还能与显著更大的开源模型（如GLM-4.6V、Qwen3-VL-Thinking）以及顶级专有模型（如Gemini 2.5 Pro和Seed-1.5-VL）相媲美甚至超越。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/step3-vl\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/step3-vl</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：Sinong</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"644\" data-imgfileid=\"100017706\" data-ratio=\"0.5564814814814815\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1158\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f6e78510&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzdY4WicrXJrlGN01A1QAH2pDcA3NBtRCuEntiawYXcvyZXrflUt2eFcibAVg60dA8sjLsNWu55qKtpg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Sinong（司农）大语言模型是面向通用农业领域的垂直大模型，依托南京农业大学的学科特色，收集了动物科学、农业经济管理等多个细分学科的大规模领域数据，总量超过40亿token。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">通过结合</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">视觉模型</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">与</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">大语言模型</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，整理和整合多源异构数据，形成高质量的农业基础数据集。项目通过合成数据构建、指令微调与强化学习等方法，提升模型的农业语言能力与领域知识。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/sinong\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/sinong</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">④项目：e2e</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"486\" data-imgfileid=\"100017705\" data-ratio=\"0.4212962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1154\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5938fe75&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzdY4WicrXJrlGN01A1QAH2pdeZvehO3bIdcKqibZZSRfTue1eQZbBSoFKy3n5icDAgRiaB3qdONxL74Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★e2e该项目提供了一个在长上下文中进行端到端测试时训练的JAX实现。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">项目将长上下文语言建模视为一个</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">连续学习问题</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，而非架构设计问题。使用标准的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">Transformer</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">架构，通过滑动窗口注意力机制进行上下文压缩，并在测试时通过下一个词预测继续学习。项目在训练时通过元学习改进模型初始化，使得在测试时的学习更为高效。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/e2e-2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/e2e-2</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">⑤项目：UAE</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"804\" data-imgfileid=\"100017708\" data-ratio=\"0.6953703703703704\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1156\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d3d30b4e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzdY4WicrXJrlGN01A1QAH2pdgImrj9zo0v9zVNtzbiaia0Do8KblagXYJeIxXjhiaZjgR6AQDVic59QCQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★UAE项目旨在通过统一自编码方法协调语义和像素表示。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目由南洋理工大学的S-Lab和商汤科技研究团队合作开发，提供了一种创新的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">图像处理技术</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，能够在多种数据集上实现高效的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">图像重建</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">表示学习</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/uae\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/uae</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;text-indent: 0px;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">📊 数据指令</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：OctoCodingBench</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"620\" data-imgfileid=\"100017707\" data-ratio=\"0.5351851851851852\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1158\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6ca9bbf3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzdY4WicrXJrlGN01A1QAH2pTOs4Beq8iboze4rrxtDGhOlpZ7MNh6XdnkvogtpJ5e1icSggO4C8iajRg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★OctoCodingBench是一个由MiniMaxAI提供的数据集，主要用于文本生成任务。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该数据集以</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">JSON</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">格式提供，包含少于1K的数据量，适用于代码生成和评估任务。数据集的目标是为代码生成模型提供一个</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">基准测试环境</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，以便更好地评估模型的性能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/octocodingbench\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/octocodingbench</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文速览了阶跃星辰开源的音频推理模型 Step-Audio-R1.1 和多模态模型 STEP3-VL，以及农业大模型 Sinong、长上下文测试项目 e2e、图像处理项目 UAE 和代码生成数据集 OctoCodingBench。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文速览了阶跃星辰开源的音频推理模型 Step-Audio-R1.1 和多模态模型 STEP3-VL，以及农业大模型 Sinong、长上下文测试项目 e2e、图像处理项目 UAE 和代码生成数据集 OctoCodingBench。",
  "summary": "本文汇总了阶跃星辰（Step-Audio-R1.1 及 STEP3-VL）以及其他机构在 AI 模型和数据集方面发布的最新进展。Step-Audio-R1.1 是原生音频推理增强模型，以 96.4%的准确率登顶全球语音推理榜单，解决了长推理性能下降问题，并支持实时流式交互。STEP3-VL 是一个轻量级 10B 参数多模态开源模型，在多模态理解和推理方面超越了多个大型竞品。此外，文章还介绍了南京农业大学的通用农业领域垂直大模型 Sinong，其利用大量农业数据训练并结合视听能力。e2e 项目是关于长上下文端到端测试的 JAX 实现，而 UAE 项目则专注于统一自编码的图像处理技术。文章还提及了 MinMaxAI 提供的用于代码生成和评估的数据集 OctoCodingBench。整体来看，文章是关于 AI 领域最新研究动态和开源项目的速览。",
